# Common ggplot2 Style Patterns

## Theme Selection Guide

| Original Chart Style | Recommended Base Theme |
|---------------------|------------------------|
| Clean white background | `theme_bw()` |
| Minimal grid lines | `theme_minimal()` |
| Classic academic look | `theme_classic()` |
| Dark background | `theme_dark()` |
| Publication-ready | `theme_cowplot()` |

## Color Palette Patterns

### Nature Journal Style
```r
nature_colors <- c("#E64B35", "#4DBBD5", "#00A087", "#3C5488", 
                   "#F39B7F", "#8491B4", "#91D1C2", "#DC0000")
```

### Science Journal Style
```r
science_colors <- c("#3B4992", "#EE0000", "#008B45", "#631879",
                    "#008280", "#BB0021", "#5F559B", "#A20056")
```

### Nature Publishing Group Palette
```r
npg_colors <- c("#E64B35", "#4DBBD5", "#00A087", "#3C5488",
                "#F39B7F", "#8491B4", "#91D1C2", "#DC0000", "#7E6148")
```

### JAMA Style
```r
jama_colors <- c("#374E55", "#DF8F44", "#00A1D5", "#B24745", 
                 "#79AF12", "#6A6599", "#80796B", "#0AB398")
```

## Typography Patterns

### Serif Font (Nature/Science)
```r
theme(
  text = element_text(family = "serif"),
  plot.title = element_text(size = 12, face = "bold"),
  axis.title = element_text(size = 10),
  axis.text = element_text(size = 8)
)
```

### Sans-serif Font (PLOS/IEEE)
```r
theme(
  text = element_text(family = "sans"),
  plot.title = element_text(size = 14, face = "bold"),
  axis.title = element_text(size = 12),
  axis.text = element_text(size = 10)
)
```

## Layout Patterns

### Minimal Grid
```r
theme(
  panel.grid.major = element_line(color = "grey90", linewidth = 0.2),
  panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
  panel.background = element_rect(fill = "white")
)
```

### No Grid (Classic)
```r
theme_classic() +
theme(
  axis.line = element_line(linewidth = 0.5),
  axis.ticks = element_line(linewidth = 0.3)
)
```

### Publication Ready
```r
theme_bw() +
theme(
  panel.grid.major = element_line(color = "grey90", linewidth = 0.2),
  panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
  panel.border = element_rect(color = "black", fill = NA, linewidth = 0.5),
  axis.line = element_line(color = "black", linewidth = 0.3),
  legend.position = "top",
  strip.background = element_rect(fill = "grey95")
)
```

## Common Scale Functions

### Discrete Colors
```r
scale_color_manual(values = c("#E64B35", "#4DBBD5", "#00A087"))
scale_fill_manual(values = c("#E64B35", "#4DBBD5", "#00A087"))
```

### Continuous Color
```r
scale_color_viridis_c(option = "plasma")
scale_fill_viridis_c(option = "viridis")
```

### Size Scale
```r
scale_size_continuous(range = c(1, 5))
scale_size_manual(values = c(2, 4, 6))
```

## Facet Patterns

### Single Row
```r
facet_wrap(~variable, nrow = 1)
```

### Grid Layout
```r
facet_grid(row_var ~ col_var, scales = "free_y")
```

## Legend Patterns

### Top Legend
```r
theme(legend.position = "top", legend.box = "horizontal")
```

### Right Legend (Default)
```r
theme(legend.position = "right")
```

### No Legend
```r
theme(legend.position = "none")
```

## Axis Patterns

### Log Scale
```r
scale_y_continuous(trans = "log10")
```

### Percent Format
```r
scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent)
```

### Breaks Control
```r
scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 100, by = 20))
```
